      <title>阿诺特：有争议的选举创造了购买机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-09/-contentious-election-creates-a-buying-opportunity-research-affiliates-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Research Affiliates 创始人兼董事长 Rob Arnott 讨论了债券收益率的前景以及美国大选对股市的影响。“在竞争激烈的选举中，股市在选举前夕举步维艰，而在选举前一周左右开始上涨，”Arnott 在接受彭博电视采访时表示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-09/-contentious-election-creates-a-buying-opportunity-research-affiliates-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 10:32:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
